commit.message:
rtnl: Use getifaddrs() to get local IP address

Use getifaddrs() instead of unstable and complex libnetlink.  This fixes
getting IP addresses on systems with recent iproute2 versions
(and without it).

commit.message: ssl: Support LibreSSL-2.7 API (compatible with OpenSSL-1.1)
Bump to 0.3.3
rtnl: Fix linking to libmnl for newer versions of libnetlink
ssl: Do not use OpenSSL-1.1 API when LibreSSL is used

ssl: Use new generate code only for OpenSSL-1.1

It apparently does not work for 1.0.2n.

SSL: Fix incorrect refcounting for the RSA key

EVP_PKEY_assign_RSA() does not increment the refcount on the RSA key,
so it gets really freed when the unique pointer goes out of scope.
Use EVP_PKEY_set1_RSA() which does increment the refcount.

Closes: https://github.com/mgorny/pshs/pull/2

SSL: Compatibility with OpenSSL 1.1.0

Stop using deprecated/removed APIs when compiling against OpenSSL >= 1.1.0.
Switch to RSA_generate_key_ex() when compiling against OpenSSL >= 1.0.0.
Bump to 0.3.2
help: Remove duplicate doc for --ssl and --no-upnp

getopt: Fix missing '-r' short option

Closes: https://github.com/mgorny/pshs/issues/1
Bump to 0.3.1
